        パラメータ:
        aUserId - User id of Twitter account
        aScreenName - Screen name of Twitter account
        aConsumerKey - Consumer key of registered application in Twitter developer site
        aConsumerSecret - Consumer secret of registered application in Twitter developer site
        anAccessToken - Access token that can be obtained in the OAuth authentication
        anAccessTokenSecret - Access token secret that can be obtained in the OAuth authentication
